<paragraph blockId="11.[170,775,869,1754]" pageId="11" pageNumber="3201">Remarks: Though quite strict graminivorous and capable of causing considerable damage to grain crops, very many plants belonging to different families have been recorded as food.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[170,775,869,1754]" pageId="11" pageNumber="3201">Natural enemies: It is sometimes heavily infested with mites.</paragraph>
